credit.credit-words: "...The fire shall try every man's work of what sort it is" (I Corinthians 3:1 3).
"We should make daily advancement in the work of character-building. When we try to separate from us our sinful habits,
if we would become fit temples for the indwel ing of the Holy Spirit. If we make an entire surrender to Him,
leave our life of sin and passion and pride, and cling to Christ and His merits,
He wil fulfil to us that He has promised."
